No. 603. The Cleveland-Cliffs Iron Company, Petitioner, v. The East Itasca Mining Company. April 15, 1907. Mr. William P. Belden and Mr. Horace Andrews for petitioner. Mr. J. L. Washburn for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Eighth.Circuit denied.
